elements.title: Camilo Cienfuegos
elements.contents: ... that after his movement's victory in the Cuban Revolution, television broadcasts showed Camilo Cienfuegos (pictured) freeing parrots from birdcages, declaring that the birds had "a right to liberty"?

elements.title: Shakespeare garden in Wessington Springs, South Dakota
elements.contents: ... that the Shakespeare garden in Wessington Springs, South Dakota, was the first of its kind in the state?

elements.title: Mihail Moxa

elements.title: Rodney, Mississippi
elements.contents: ... that Rodney, Mississippi, became a ghost town after the Mississippi River shifted about two miles (3.2 km) away?

elements.title: a Holocaust memoir translated in 2023

elements.title: a Taylor Swift song

elements.title: Robert L. McLeod
